    Responsibilities included grading, holding office hours, and teaching three back-to-back review sections on fridays. 
    %
    Also assisted teaching for undergraduate \textit{``Compilers''} and graduate \textit{``Advanced Compilers''}, helping to design assignments
    (including open and closed test suites), grading, and 
