    Worked for a startup co-founded by Prof. Eric Wills (from the University of Oregon). 
    %
    Setup a Solr-based search engine in Java and wrote Python scripts to manage MySQL databases, translation spreadsheets for site-localization, and simple image analyses, among other projects.
